      <title>Citrix 母公司希望通过 41 亿美元的贷款重新定价来节省资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/citrix-parent-eyes-savings-through-4-1-billion-loan-repricing</link>
