      <title>随着外汇紧缩的缓解，埃及通胀再次放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/egypt-inflation-keeps-slowing-as-foreign-currency-crunch-eases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及通胀在 4 月份连续第二个月放缓，因为最近的货币浮动后外汇供应增加似乎缓解了这个中东人口最多的国家的物价压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/egypt-inflation-keeps-slowing-as-foreign-currency-crunch-eases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 05:40:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
